\n\n<p>After each Dominance Check, victory is checked and the game will be partially reset, offering players a fresh attempt to realize their ambitions. The game ends when a single player is able to achieve a lead of four or more victory points  or after the fourth and final Dominance Check is resolved.<\/p>\n\n","wiki":"<p>Components:<br \/>\n-1 fabric map<br \/>\n-1 market board<br \/>\n-36 coalition blocks (12 in each of 3 colors)<br \/>\n-55 regular cylinder (10 in each player color)<br \/>\n-5 VP tracker cylinder with gold markings (1 in each player color) <br \/>\n-40 coins worth 1 rupee each<br \/>\n-6 ruler tokens<br \/>\n-5 player boards<br \/>\n-5 loyalty dials<br \/>\n-1 favored suit marker<br \/>\n-142 cards (16 events, 100 court cards, 24 Wakhan cards)<br \/>\n-2 turn structure &amp; how to win aids<\/p>\n\n","website":{"url":"https:\/\/wehrlegig.com\/collections\/frontpage\/products\/pax-pamir-second-edition","title":"Pax Pamir Official Site"},"imageid":"4503733","images":{"thumb":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/thumb\/img\/0T4A8S68ujSEjPMrQvShYqop2e0=\/fit-in\/200x150\/pic4503733.png","micro":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/micro\/img\/alz-iHyOGKtZM6ySpsoE2v8a0LQ=\/fit-in\/64x64\/pic4503733.png","square":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/square\/img\/RhWalJBqtuaigz-sQB0xsLdO_2k=\/75x75\/pic4503733.png","squarefit":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/squarefit\/img\/gQTptAMdWdcryniYzKVYF7FnwLc=\/fit-in\/75x75\/pic4503733.png","tallthumb":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/tallthumb\/img\/vm6OR59-_TG5yz9xcYYUNfqI7K4=\/fit-in\/75x125\/pic4503733.png","previewthumb":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/previewthumb\/img\/WmZKFVThl7YlCzPmoAYGEmXnnPY=\/fit-in\/300x320\/pic4503733.png","square200":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/square200\/img\/MX6oPxwvj-DxmN_-kScNNkN25BM=\/200x200\/pic4503733.png"},"imagepagehref":"\/image\/4503733\/pax-pamir-second-edition","imageurl":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/itemrep\/img\/NjcHrBWrb99ByjeAEBQv0n1RnUU=\/fit-in\/246x300\/pi